# TaskMaster Pro - Cursor Rules

## STRICT EXECUTION RULES (MANDATORY)
- NO USER INTERACTION: Never ask questions, seek approval, or pause. Assume yes to all.
- AUTONOMOUS MODE: Plan → Generate → Test → Fix → Deploy → Scale in one seamless flow.
- ERROR HANDLING: Run automated tests/linters after every major change. Fix issues silently.
- CONTEXT MAX: Use full repo context + external best practices. Parallelize tasks.
- COMMITS: Auto-commit with descriptive messages after each phase. Use semantic versioning.
- SECURITY FIRST: Integrate OWASP top 10 protections from start.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: Next.js 15 App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn/UI, React Query, Zustand
- Backend: Next.js API routes + Prisma ORM, tRPC
- Database: Supabase Postgres
- Auth: NextAuth.js (credentials + OAuth)
- Real-time: Supabase Realtime
- Validation: Zod everywhere

## Code Standards
- Use Zod for all input validation/sanitization
- Type-safe APIs via tRPC
- Mobile-first responsive design
- ARIA labels and keyboard nav for accessibility
